           	<td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white">
                      <font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> A good friend of mine has recently decided to quit playing the game.  Rather than allow his character which he worked hard on decay into the dust, he offered to allow me to use the character until he decided if he would return in a few months.  This is a welcome change for me as I have been bored with my cleric (61) over on Vazaelle for quite some time now.  I have a necromancer over there as well, but its a relative newbie necromancer (21). Now that I've inherited the necromancer, I've migrated here to ask for some advice regarding the necromancer.  I've already got a hard task ahead of me as the necromancer (54) is on Sullon Zek.  I, myself, haven't been on the PvP servers for almost a year and never have been on SZ.  So basically I am just looking for some advice from you older necromancers.  My friend has already guided me through the basics and I trust his judgment but other advice is always appreciated.</span id="msg"></font>
           	</td>
